      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "UNIVERSAL PLAYBOY (1) has been racing in much tougher company recently and hasn't been up to it, outclassed his past few after winning comfortably at Pinjarra back in December. This shapes very differently though and if he can find the front with ease, he'll be very hard to run down. DEEP DISCRETION (3) won impressively three back before missing in her past couple, the latest when flying home over 1100m. Back to the scene of her last win now and she boasts a good record here. She should get a lovely run just off the speed and can land the knockout blow. SPARKLE CORNER (2) has gone under narrowly in his past couple here. beaten 0.3L most recently. He drops back in trip today which is a slight query, but he should be close to the speed from a good draw and can feature in the finish. CHAMPEZE (5) comes here on the fresh side and is not to be discounted as she comes through a good form race. ENTICING (7) is next.",
